title: [Alaramis's Weaponry]
[Alaramis's Outfitting]
description: A woven floral tapestry hangs on one of the warped driftwood walls, and a warped driftwood ceiling rises overhead.  An ornate bottled ship sits in one corner of a warped driftwood floor.  There is some carved haon pegs on one side of the shop and a wide knotted oak counter on the other.
